{
  "chapter": 308,
  "chapter_summary": "本章分两条线索展开。寇仲在郁林郡与宋鲁会面，得知宋玉致拒绝他的真正原因并非宋阀主将他名字刻在磨刀石上，而是宋阀内部存在主战与主和两派之争——宋智为首的主战派力主北上争霸，宋师道和宋玉致则主张保境安民，不愿岭南子弟为战争流血。宋阀主态度暧昧，两不表态。寇仲当即表示不需宋家一兵一卒，只要物资支援，便立志打天下后回来迎娶玉致，随后随宋鲁赶往宋家山城。与此同时，徐子陵化名弓辰春在乌江帮船上遭遇合一派掌门\"通天姥姥\"夏妙莹及其弟子\"美姬\"丝娜追击。原来弓辰春曾始乱终弃夏妙莹的大弟子致其含恨而死，丝娜更是其继承人。霍纪童随行出战被徐子陵一招击退，丝娜提出三招之约，徐子陵应允。雷九指主动表态愿共同进退。宋家山城地势险峻，寇仲抵达后被宋智引往磨刀堂见宋阀主。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "鲁叔怎知我在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "郁林是我宋家的地头，有甚么风吹草动，都瞒不过我们；更何况我是专诚在此恭候大驾，只不过给你先遇上玉致吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "鲁叔既见过玉致，当知我为何要到这里喝酒，她刻下是否在城中？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲你勿要怪她。她是为一个难以启齿的原因，才硬起心肠拒绝你，我也是最近始知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "她已告诉我，宋阀主把我的名字刻在磨刀石上。唉！是否具有此事呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "此事的确不假，我曾亲口问过大兄，他却笑而不语，令人莫测高深，不过我指她拒绝你的事，却与此无关。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "那究竟是为甚么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "她不想因你而使我宋家直接卷入争霸天下的纷争中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "在我们宋家内，对天下的形势有两种看法，一系认为此乃振兴宋家的最佳时机，此系可称为主战派，以宋智为首，力主以岭南为基地，再向长江扩展，建立一个以南人为主的皇朝，至不济也可和北人平分秋色。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "另一系当然是主和派，只要宋家能稳保岭南，由于有重洋高山偏阻之险，无论谁人得天下，都只能采羁糜的政策，山高皇帝远，宋家等若划地为主。只有别人要买你们的账，只不知此派以何人为主？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "就是师道和玉致，而我则认为两种策略均属可行。但师道和玉致却不忍岭南唯我们马首是瞻的俚民，为我们的荣枯抛头颅洒热血。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "那阀主他老人家究竟倾向那一派的主张？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他从来没表示过立场。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "怎会是这样的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大兄的行事从来都是令人难解的。一方面任由宋智招募兵员，进行种种训练和做战争的准备功夫；另一方面又指时机未至，要宋智按兵不动。现在你该明白为何智兄对你和玉致的事那么热心，而玉致明明对你情深似海，却仍要摆出对你无情的样儿，致纠缠不清。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "来！敬鲁叔一杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "我现在快乐得想对酒高歌一曲，原来致致心内是喜欢我的。这事不难解决，若我真能得天下，便来迎娶致致，不幸战败身亡，此事自然作废。我根本不用你们一兵一卒，只需你们物资上援助我就成。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "此事关系重大，必须大兄点头才行。问题是他既把你的名字刻在磨刀石上，照惯例你已成为他目标对手，让你去见他实吉凶难料，所以玉致才要阻止你去见他，智兄也为此事烦恼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "致致在那里呢？我想先见她一面。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "她已返回山城，我亦是收到山城的飞鸽快讯，才知你和她碰过头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "我们立即到山城去，一刻我都不愿再等哩！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竟有个老婆婆在船上，不知是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓爷的眼力真了得，这婆子是否一头白发，手执拂尘？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "确像拿着柄似拂尘的东西，这位老人家是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不会吧？通天姥姥夏妙莹一向不问江湖的事，霍纪童虽是她的谊子，亦该请不动她。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "她旁边尚有个苗女，长得相当美貌。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那定是巴盟的'美姬'丝娜，她是夏妙莹的得意弟子，更是合一派的继承人，听说夏妙莹将于短期内把派主之位让给她。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "合一派和巴盟都是我们乌江帮惹不起的大帮大派，这趟恐怕连我们沙老大都罩不住。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "果然是你弓辰春，我还以为你死了哩！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "林香主把船驶近岸边，我上岸和她们把事情解决吧！你不用理我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓爷分明不认识夏妙莹，为何她却像和弓爷是老相识的样子。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "此事一言难尽，情况紧迫，林香主请把船驶近陆岸吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓爷有多少成把握应付对方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "很难说，若他们一起出手，胜败难料，但脱身该没有问题。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "通天姥姥乃一派之主，绝不会和其他人联手群攻，弓爷既有此自信，便待他们过来时在手底下见个真章，请恕我们不能插手，弓爷见谅。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "林香主非常够朋友。此事无论如何发展，我弓辰春绝不会把贵帮牵涉在内。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓兄若不嫌弃，小弟愿与弓兄共同进退。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "群山萦绕，郁水环流，崎岖险阻，纵使我有数万精兵，恐亦难有用武之地。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这山城耗用了不知多少人力物力，仍要历三代百多年时间，才建成现在这般规模。城内长期储备超过一年的粮食，又有泉水，清甜可口，泡茶更是一绝。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "那我定要多喝两口哩！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "山城的建设，主要贪其奇险难下，但若没有郁林郡的富足，那山城只徒具雄奇之表，现在则可相辅相乘，且兼水陆交通之利，可通达全国。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋智",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "阀主有命，请少帅立即到磨刀堂见他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "雷兄万勿插手，弓某人自有方法应付。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "text": "姥姥仙驾既临，我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "少说闲话。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓辰春你的胆子真大，龟缩这么多年后，竟敢大摇大摆的到散花楼作乐，是否欺我夏妙莹老得忘掉你以前的所作所为，不再和你计较。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_na",
      "speaker_name": "丝娜",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "大师姊因你始乱终弃，至含郁而死，你弓辰春万死不足以辞其咎。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_si_na",
      "text": "内中情况异常复杂，诸位可否听我解释。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "speaker_name": "霍纪童",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "只看你闻死讯而毫无悲戚之情，立知你弓辰春是个无情无义，狠心狗肺之徒。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "text": "霍纪童你能好到那里去，成都给你既奸且弃的女子数不胜数，阿大别说阿二啦！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "speaker_name": "霍纪童",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "text": "你若能挡我三招，弓某愿束手就擒，任凭处置，但若挡不了，你们须立即退走，并要答应永不再来烦我，霍纪童你有资格作主吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "speaker_name": "霍纪童",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "废话！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "text": "纪童退下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_na",
      "speaker_name": "丝娜",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "假如你能在三招内令我落败，我们立即掉头走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_si_na",
      "text": "一言为定，若弓某人三招内不能赢你，就束手就擒，绝不食言。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_na",
      "speaker_name": "丝娜",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓辰春你确是傲气可嘉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 308,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "是否想反悔哩！",
      "tone": "厉声",
